WEBVTT

1
02:27:43.021 --> 02:27:44.662
Why you take so long?

2
02:27:46.068 --> 02:27:48.127
I knock and I knock.

3
02:27:50.821 --> 02:27:51.945
Grace. the door.

4
02:27:51.984 --> 02:27:53.141
Close the door.

5
02:27:57.267 --> 02:27:59.509
I make door.
You close door.

6
02:28:17.354 --> 02:28:18.340
Yes.

7
02:28:28.006 --> 02:28:30.555
I ask Adrian to work on this.

8
02:28:41.966 --> 02:28:44.556
You no want it
sunnier than this?

9
02:28:57.251 --> 02:28:58.159
Grace.

10
02:29:00.468 --> 02:29:03.302
Eridian scientists
are ready...

11
02:29:03.345 --> 02:29:05.596
to prepare Hail Mary
for journey home.

12
02:29:16.417 --> 02:29:18.858
Yes. think about
it long time.
